  "Description": "Build s&box games by talking to Claude. 99 tools to drive the s&box editor through conversation — GameObjects, scripts, scenes, components, physics, networking, UI, world-gen, type discovery. v1.3.x is stable on current s&box builds (fixed bootstrap crash, dock-independent RPCs, smarter hierarchy query). If you use Claude Code, install the companion plugin: `/plugin marketplace add LouSputthole/Sbox-Claude` then `/plugin install sbox-claude` — it bundles the MCP server registration plus an `sbox-build-feature` skill that codifies the screenshot-driven iteration workflow. See TROUBLESHOOTING.md if anything misbehaves.",
